dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Samuel Diaz. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Samuel. My name is Kimberly Allen.
It's great to meet you, Kimberly. Could you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five eight two four seven nine.
Thank you, Kimberly. Additionally, I will need to verify your date of birth. Could you please provide me with that information as well?
Of course. My date of birth is December twenty third, nineteen eighty five.
Thank you for confirming that, Kimberly. Your account details are now verified. How can I assist you today?
I need to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can certainly help you with that, Kimberly. Let's proceed with adding the new vehicle to your policy.
Thank you for your time, Kimberly. Have a great day!
